  "title": "Toggled element still displays in current refined values when false",
  "body": "We're currently using a toggle widget to display hits flagged as a 'special'. On initial render it shows up in the current refined values even when false. Once it is removed it then works correctly.\n\ne.g.\n\n<img width=\"315\" alt=\"screen shot 2016-03-07 at 22 24 57\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1872727/13568153/7b3208ac-e4b3-11e5-9d7c-c518d8a5b408.png\">\n",
